# 3-Month Roadmap


## **Month 1 — Foundations**
### Goals:
- Data ingestion pipeline
- Auto-categorization MVP
- Dashboard baseline

### Deliverables:
- CSV/API import
- Categorization engine (rule-based)
- Portfolio allocation view
- Initial risk scoring


## **Month 2 — Automation Engine**
### Goals:
- Smart alerts system
- Drift detection
- Alert prioritization logic

### Deliverables:
- Alert bundles
- “Why this matters” explanations
- Alert settings page
- Notification system
  

## **Month 3 — Rebalancing & Reports**
### Goals:
- Rebalancing suggestions
- Monthly automation report
- Impact simulation

### Deliverables:
- Rebalance engine MVP
- Before/After simulation card
- Stability score tracking
- Monthly PDF report
